  <dataqual>
    <attracc>
      <attraccr>Values from the interpolated elevation raster were extracted for each input data point and compared to the original input value to assess reproducibility at each point. Average difference between the raster and the input data point value was 0.3 ft, with a median of 0.01 ft, standard deviation of 8.3 ft, and maximum difference of 106 ft.</attraccr>
    </attracc>
